        categories: ["In Home Care Blog"],
        excerpt: "Catalina Elwell and Laura Lara represented Cerna at the City of Hope Health Fair on May, 13, 2015. City of Hope is a leader in the fight to conquer cancer,",
        image: "/assets/blog/blogimage68.webp",
        seoTitle: "City of Hope Health Fair | Cerna Homecare",
