        html: "<img src=\"http://www.cernahealth.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-o-matic/cache/a14d5_UnmaskBlogStamp.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"User Conference 2011\" class=\"alignRight\" style=\"float: right;\" />Here at <a title=\"HEALTHCAREfirst\" href=\"http://www.healthcarefirst.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HEALTHCARE<em>first</em></a>, it is all about our clients&hellip;and why shouldn&rsquo;t it be? They are the reason we are all here! That is why we are pleased to announce our upcoming User Conference, to be held on June 9th &amp; 10th at the Hilton New Orleans Riverside hotel in New Orleans, LA.\n<p><strong><em>Let the good times roll</em></strong> as you and your peers learn tips and tricks to maximize the performance and usefulness of our software solutions and services. <strong><em>Unmask </em></strong>information with unparalleled access to HEALTHCARE<em>first</em> executives, product management, training and support team members and even industry experts who will help you grow your knowledge, skills and expertise:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bill Dombi, NAHC Vice President for Law (<em>invited</em>)</li>\n<li>Kenny Hulshof, former MO Congressman</li>\n<li>Martha Tecca, Deyta</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><em>Get</em></strong> <strong><em>Jazzed</em></strong> as we unveil our new merged solution, client-driven enhancements, and updates to the system that are geared towards making your agency run more efficiently, allowing you to <em>spend more time focusing on your PATIENTS and less time on PAPERWORK</em>.</p>\n<p>Whether you are an end-user or in Agency Management, this conference marks the ideal opportunity for you to network with other agencies and gain more insight into our products, all while enjoying the fun and excitement of New Orleans. See you in June!</p>",
